    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Transparency in Student Lending Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends title IV (Student Assistance) of the Higher Education Act of 1965 to expand disclosure requirements for an institution of higher education (IHE) that participates in the Direct Loan program. Specifically, it requires an IHE to disclose, in federal student loan application materials, the annual percentage rate applicable to a Direct Loan. </p>]]></text>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <updateDate>2016-07-14T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
